%h1 Advanced decks

%p
    Each advanced deck introduces a second color to the deck, and expands on the first deck's theme.

%p
    Each color appears twice in the whole series.

%ul
    %li White plus blue: enchantments and tempo
    %li Blue plus green: illusion and bigger creatures
    %li Black plus white: vampires and sacrifice
    %li Red plus black: goblins
    %li Green plus red: ramp and burn